Toast bread, if desired. Combine mayonnaise, mustard and steak sauce in small bowl. Spread mayonnaise mixture evenly over 1 side of each bread slice. Equally layer 1/2 of Baked Ham, Smoked Ham, Oven Roasted Turkey, Smoked Chicken, tomatoes, lettuce and cheese on 4 bread slices. Top each with another bread slice. Repeat layers; top each with remaining bread slice. Secure sandwiches with frilled toothpicks.